    "Transposed-Attention Map (A) Multi Deep Learning for Image RestorationImage restoration aims to recover its clean counterparts from a degraded image.",
    "A popular scheme is to use CNN structures to learn efficient models to capture local features of images and learn generalizable image priors.",
    "CNNs have been widely used in various image restoration tasks, including image denoising [3,26], demosaicing [14,31], and super-resolution [19,32].",
